e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73400c4dac21cf9391506f7eea013566095f9843","tid":350900,"uid":6481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>milktop好食好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同道中人<br />\n我成日推介俾frd都冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講起milktop嘅話<br />\n比較欣賞佢啲布甸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包裝又靚又夠滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到有得買？"},{"pid":"148da96f7e232a515ce5ad511c717c3d948166b3","tid":350900,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"雀巢啲濕鳩product就算吧啦"},{"pid":"fb1b38685d1e31f6448b022f794356066b8e0339","tid":350900,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"有冇曲奇味"},{"pid":"81c593bf51a7c42c2efb30b74415937426738549","tid":350900,"uid":27728,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"如果拎movepick同哈根大師比 只有價錢相近/包裝好睇<br />\n<br />\n口感/味道我都覺得哈根大師過幾班 <br />\n<br />\n就似雲呢拿呢個最接近雪糕base既口味  哈根大師食落去係好實好有口感（甜唔甜就因人而異），movepick食落就知好輕身  因該雪糕做個陣會打入空氣 打得越多雪糕就越多 成本就越平  <br />\n<br />\n利申 研究左6年雪糕  從事呢方面既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef76a7d41f499dd6316bdd0032f5bce4450e0096","tid":350900,"uid":11629,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"講口味哈根大真係多好多冇咁易食悶<br />\n但movenpick個朱古力味真係屌打哈根大"},{"pid":"a0453ff504b4b8c28a91b78eb7c2d351e2955e9c","tid":350900,"uid":70876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d2210f5b3af0db8e1a177903c5b6a891359e36","tid":350900,"uid":130084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:27:32.000Z","msg":"未食過"},{"pid":"811fdd69dbeddae60ca9793da464630c41f461ef","tid":350900,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>movenpick vanilla贏九條街，最重要係佢乳脂少，口感清新<br />\n越平嘅雪糕係越多乳脂，相反人地植物原料多就係粗，你班懵撚係唔識食</blockquote><br />\n咁又點？口感差就係差，話知佢食完可以減肥"},{"pid":"7c59b381d0bc563b7259f4676c0d504a03565166","tid":350900,"uid":84472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"有冇人食過惠康牌嗰隻雪糕"},{"pid":"30de56171d8817942017011422a9b8a9f1d829dd","tid":350900,"uid":14478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"Movenpick 軟啲<br />\nHaagen Dazs 好硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8161fa80f0d5357e955e0b88595ce8730802bb1","tid":350900,"uid":22743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"以最普通既vanilla黎計<br />\n<br />\n哈根贏口感 夠滑同實 moven 就仲有啲細冰粒係雪糕入面<br />\n<br />\nmoven贏香味同味道 啲vanilla 味出好多"},{"pid":"6710cb4c8d9ab1464c7f53f1f7e33a8f382ed05e","tid":350900,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以最普通既vanilla黎計<br />\n<br />\n哈根贏口感 夠滑同實 moven 就仲有啲細冰粒係雪糕入面<br />\n<br />\nmoven贏香味同味道 啲vanilla 味出好多</blockquote><br />\n有細冰粒既雪糕係唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7ace3d1a915514e961452d2d5622bb2bb91b23","tid":350900,"uid":126415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Connoisseur No. 1 好食又性價比高！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncaramel honey macadamia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCookies and cream <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50627392ca7b10113b70a41fbd76977a7ce202b","tid":350900,"uid":14201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"好膩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15eec71de8761a0c16437e5ea2818709ea9e8a34","tid":350900,"uid":128085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>milktop好食好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同道中人<br />\n我成日推介俾frd都冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講起milktop嘅話<br />\n比較欣賞佢啲布甸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包裝又靚又夠滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <br />\n食過milktop 無再食其他<br />\n哈根甜撚到仆街"},{"pid":"63f61f726a7d16fa09e16093c92319a9f6579370","tid":350900,"uid":6116,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/130905_3d16e8ffe7bc22fe585981ae339e6abb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F130905_3d16e8ffe7bc22fe585981ae339e6abb.jpg&h=0f1f051c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老屎忽應該食過呢隻<br />\n我覺得好味過你地講個兩隻大牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個好易就買到 而家難買左好多 <br />\n七十幾蚊盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cadab0964b6dd8f536bc4297434d45051f2020","tid":350900,"uid":14478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"Movenpick 大盒好食過細盒 唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058495b62eaafbd60e2d7b2eddf8031b6cb89347","tid":350900,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"喺7仔平嗰時買過一杯食<br />\n奶油味好撚重，好撚油<br />\n完全唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd906a9eb02cf7745eda9723614f3ee387f661f","tid":350900,"uid":86127,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"Movenpick Vanilla 入面有雲呢拿籽 你地見到雪糕入面啲一粒粒就係 所以佢個種香味係同其他雪糕有唔同<br />\n<br />\nStrawberry 係比較無咁多人鐘意 因為佢用新鮮果肉 係比較酸 陣酸味已經蓋過左其他<br />\n<br />\n而Swiss Chocolate入面有唔甜既朱古力碎 少少苦 但好香<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得Movenpick chocolate 係咁多品牌之中最好食，而vanilla 就係誠意之作，strawberry 就好麻麻<br />\n另外 Panna cotta , Stracciatella 都可以一戰<br />\n鐘意酸既朋友可以試下Lemon &amp; Lime<br />\n個味好正 但口感一般<br />\n<br />\nBtw感覺上家庭裝無門市/酒店咁好食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 打手，五年前做過屯市Movenpick"},{"pid":"1cc7e148b5535f95f17a46e056da7339d6ac7e40","tid":350900,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>milktop好食好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同道中人<br />\n我成日推介俾frd都冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講起milktop嘅話<br />\n比較欣賞佢啲布甸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包裝又靚又夠滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <br />\n食過milktop 無再食其他<br />\n哈根甜撚到仆街</blockquote><br />\n鹽味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd33d70d662d068e147cc93011903a8d64d42ba","tid":350900,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>milktop好食好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同道中人<br />\n我成日推介俾frd都冇人識<img src=\"/assets/fac