900,"uid":21514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"老母成日買movenpick同haagendazs<br />\n我揀movenpick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa259a557dad901220b23d6792a26ec8ce14589c","tid":350900,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"movenpick 最好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdf11527e55008dc318ca9bcef330631d466f9d","tid":350900,"uid":55594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"兩款熱情果味都買左 movenpick好食好撚多 haagen dazs好撚甜 movenpick甜度岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405165693c6da1837e76ec0b58f817ad84be1921","tid":350900,"uid":1844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"Ben&amp;Jerry's 最好食喎我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9345dcf72b228cd9f1acda0bb29a94a0f661efd","tid":350900,"uid":128127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:10:59.000Z","msg":"最中意食dreyers既杏仁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4a713ef9a9f0df0fe765cdbd3c3bc6d65c28a5","tid":350900,"uid":4085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最中意食dreyers既杏仁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n石板街都不錯 曲奇都可以一戰"},{"pid":"e4b85b1c2ca91e480004bd9a6f272b9bc60da862","tid":350900,"uid":128871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>集團黎講，movenpick同哈根兩間都係雀巢雪糕附屬品牌。去taste唔去百佳嘅分別。<br />\n<br />\n價錢嚟講，movenpick 20蚊有200幾g，哈根 20蚊得百五g，係比較平。<br />\n<br />\n以下只作雲尼嗱口味比較。<br />\n<br />\nmovenpick賣點在天然。所以雲尼嗱味真喺有啲草味。甜度比較低，味道同雀巢雪糕杯裝無咩分別。口感粗糙，不如話佢有層次同有泡沫感。打開可以見到雲呢嗱碎，唔會話完全見唔到材料咁。夠天然。個人就天然口感同味道幾加分。推薦焦糖口味。<br />\n<br />\n哈根賣點。貴。甜。大眾口味。絲滑口感，所以唔知佢喺用化學品調味，定喺完全分解或隔走啲材料。食得多其實都會感覺哈根同雀巢杯裝其實差唔多味。<br />\n<br />\n既然哈根食得多都會覺得味道厭。我唔介意買movenpick，每次享受吓個層次有泡沫嘅口感。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. Movenpick係跟nestle，只有美國哈根經營權係賣左俾nestle，由美國nestle負責生產<br />\n日本哈根就係跟日本佬係日本廠生產<br />\n其餘國家，包括香港哈根係跟General Mills，係法國廠生產<br />\n三間廠配方整法大大小小都唔同<br />\n<br />\n2. 哈根賣點係<span style=\"color: red;\">全天然材料無加任何化學品</span>，無防腐劑。滑同奶味重係因為用埋牛奶裡面最頂層個浸忌廉做穩定劑<br />\n<br />\n3. 個人口味個個唔同，但論texture, air content &amp; quality 哈根應該都屌打movenpick<br />\n哈根空氣含量得~20% movenpick或者其他牌子起碼一半都係打空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：前哈根員工 好睇唔過眼movenpick扮上菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漲知識了，多謝巴打指正"},{"pid":"e98c03b93ea3c2a43462f585e14678559470ffa6","tid":350900,"uid":128871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Movenpick 軟啲<br />\nHaagen Dazs 好硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常雪糕都有指引，要你拎出雪櫃之後等10分鐘。半融狀態，食用最佳。"},{"pid":"a5069e4fc6e36b3921b71397bdaf4ebd58764c15","tid":350900,"uid":49176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知係咪心理作用<br />\n其實食哈根大 係佢鋪頭食係正過就咁係超級市場買</blockquote><br />\n唔係心理作用<br />\n以前食哈密瓜味<br />\n鋪頭係多勁多果肉"},{"pid":"7238fcadd5adebeb512e141290af069b6c34a081","tid":350900,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解我聽都未聽過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同#2嗰個平凡少女絲打一齊啱啱放監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cbb80dd7598ea6983d92406a10f737d51966a1","tid":350900,"uid":128871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>movenpick同哈根都係Nestle都講得出<br />\n呢度係連登黎架 乜人都有<br />\n唔好以為事撚但鳩嗡兩句都過到骨啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe&nbsp;Pillsbury Company&nbsp;bought H&auml;agen-Dazs in 1983. In 1999, Pillsbury and Nestl&eacute; merged their U.S. and Canadian ice cream operations into a joint venture called Ice Cream Partners.&nbsp;General Mills, in turn, bought Pillsbury in 2001 and succeeded to its interest in the joint venture. That same year, Nestl&eacute; exercised its contractual right to buy out General Mills' interest in Ice Cream Partners, which included the right to a 99-year license for the H&auml;agen-Dazs brand<br />\n<br />\nIn April 2003, Nestl&eacute; bought the international rights for M&ouml;venpick ice cream from the hotel group, and an independent business unit called Swiss Premium Ice Cream was created. The business is now operated by a subsidiary called Nestl&eacute; Super Premium headquartered in&nbsp;Vevey&nbsp;(Switzerland)"},{"pid":"68cf03e64b9629ecac952209683cc1eea0fc59eb","tid":350900,"uid":128871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]movenpick同哈根都係Nestle都講得出<br />\n呢度係連登黎架 乜人都有<br />\n唔好以為事撚但鳩嗡兩句都過到骨啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得真喺乜人都有"},{"pid":"159011f68de6d3a5b8b8c689c39d24272da83d3c","tid":350900,"uid":202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"movenpick 朱古力最好食"},{"pid":"a2466d8980527d8dd0f52b79308a5c84aa7bc215","tid":350900,"uid":124473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"自從上年哈根搵專家dickson整左核突fb廣告之後<br />\n基本上已blacklist佢...<br />\n哈根雖然已經非常平民化, 但都叫係比其他雪糕高一個層次<br />\n攪埋d核突廣告自降身價.....<br />\n以為social media係萬能...."},{"pid":"c41f0fc7a33c187c09b2fe88600f3f546ab60690","tid":350900,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你食開💩?movepick 好食，應該冇難食既雪糕lu ！ 全部D雪糕得個粗字，士多啤梨味苦既😂點同哈根大師比?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n士多啤梨味苦既你個口係咪生癌呀？"},{"pid":"8688aa665f67097f7bea648cdc7082234c6639e7","tid":350900,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最近流行？唔識喎</blockquote><br />\n啱啱放監？</blockquote><br />\n香港有左成十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你係咪十年前出冊？"},{"pid":"a01705bb830a6ccff8544cda27fa66a38f49784a","tid":350900,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雪糕嚟講一定係阿波羅<br />\n屌打哈根大同movenpick</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n算罷啦你。"},{"pid":"1187283002c0f67d8d182a7c0d3aee0e740f166a","tid":350900,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知係咪心理作用<br />\n其實食哈根大 係佢鋪頭食係正過就咁係超級市場買</blockquote><br />\n唔係心理作用<br />\n以前食哈密瓜味<br />\n鋪頭係多勁多果肉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈密瓜味唔講都醒唔起，呢隻真係堅好味，諗諗下都停產左成十幾年，而家係得返日本間唔中做限量款。"},{"pid":"abd9d2e73c7bb33d53fe008673f5fb0ee92cae8b","tid":350900,"uid":31491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/130905_3d16e8ffe7bc22fe585981ae339e6abb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F130905_3d16e8ffe7bc22fe585981ae339e6abb.jpg&h=0f1f051c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老屎忽應該食過呢隻<br />\n我覺得好味過你地講個兩隻大牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個好易就買到 而家難買左好多 <br />\n七十幾蚊盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好想食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62d8de1ea7e4796d699483bbdc97b4661c996bd","tid":350900,