ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得好食喎。"},{"pid":"a817c90c3196677fcfeada80dd40132ce503f6d3","tid":350900,"uid":86236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"咪又係雀巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過哈根好味啲既"},{"pid":"cdcf32b787040ff560bf0c2ae636fa63eb14c176","tid":350900,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>movenpick vanilla贏九條街，最重要係佢乳脂少，口感清新<br />\n越平嘅雪糕係越多乳脂，相反人地植物原料多就係粗，你班懵撚係唔識食</blockquote><br />\n我都中意粗粒感覺<br />\n哈根大師某啲味好食 但口感好似有啲化學"},{"pid":"6483fe5c1116f88990e4ceb5d62b99094455920e","tid":350900,"uid":81156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ben&amp;Jerry's 最好食喎我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甜到仆街<br />\n唔好香港冇就吹奏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惠康唔係間唔中都有得賣?</blockquote><br />\n台灣係，香港冇聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係真係好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a32803bc12b9060412c6d8c5ad5887698c5c4df","tid":350900,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ben&amp;Jerry's 最好食喎我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甜到仆街<br />\n唔好香港冇就吹奏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惠康唔係間唔中都有得賣?</blockquote><br />\n台灣係，香港冇