r />\n早兩日我至買左兩盒<br />\n呢隻真係7，80後回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAddress plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1b619fbfb607313096cda3d34f04fdf150815a","tid":350900,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>movenpick同哈根都係Nestle都講得出<br />\n呢度係連登黎架 乜人都有<br />\n唔好以為事撚但鳩嗡兩句都過到骨啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe&amp;nbsp;Pillsbury Company&amp;nbsp;bought H&auml;agen-Dazs in 1983. In 1999, Pillsbury and Nestl&eacute; merged their U.S. and Canadian ice cream operations into a joint venture called Ice Cream Partners.&amp;nbsp;General Mills, in turn, bought Pillsbury in 2001 and succeeded to its interest in the joint venture. That same year, Nestl&eacute; exercised its contractual right to buy out General Mills' interest in Ice Cream Partners, which included the right to a 99-year license for the H&auml;agen-Dazs brand<br />\n<br />\nIn April 2003, Nestl&eacute; bought the international rights for M&ouml;venpick ice cream from the hotel group, and an independent business unit called Swiss Premium Ice Cream was created. The business is now operated by a subsidiary called Nestl&eacute; Super Premium headquartered in&amp;nbsp;Vevey&amp;nbsp;(Switzerland)</blockquote><br />\n光緒年代同土星有無資料"},{"pid":"868a34fff49051460d2913b1f237a3bf96a002f8","tid":350900,"uid":15108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩款熱情果味都買左 movenpick好食好撚多 haagen dazs好撚甜 movenpick甜度岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱情果狂熱者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMovenpick個熱情果好正 但淨係buffet食到 只見過一次aeon有得賣 其實邊到有"}]}